lawmakers said was pornographic was cancelled before it was to have 
opened at the corcoran gallery in washington 
other lawmakers have criticized the nea for supporting the work 
of artist andres serrano who depicted in a photograph jesus christ 
on a crucifix submerged in the artists urine 
