specific pay raise proopsal for congress to go along with the 
proposed limit on outside income 
bush has advocated pay raises in general for congress but has 
decided to steer clear of becoming ensnared in what is always a 
poltically treacherous issue on capitol hill deciding instead to 
let congress resolve the matter itself the sources said 
