administration disputed the environmental groups report as a major 
exaggeration of the risk sales fell immediately supermarkets began 
frequent posting of signs proclaiming their apples as alarfree and 
reducing prices on the red delicious variety on which alar 
frequently had been used 
even though epa criticized the natural resources defense council 
report the agency plans to ban use of alar and the manufacturer has 
withdrawn it from the us market 
